%% BaseComponent state/config flow (before vs after)
sequenceDiagram
  participant Caller
  participant Comp as BaseComponent
  Note right of Comp
    BEFORE: updates local const; not persisted
  end note
  Caller->>Comp: update({ size: 'lg' })
  Comp-->>Caller: getConfig() -> old variant/size
  Note over Comp: AFTER: use mutable config object; recompute styles and persist